text: Gavin Morris (born 24 October 1998) is a South African cricketer. He made his List A debut for KwaZulu-Natal in the 2016–17 CSA Provincial One-Day Challenge on 15 January 2017. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:KwaZulu- Natal cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Durban
